```

**Current formal characteristics**:
- Clean grid layouts
- Minimal spacing (`gap-2`)
- Error states use `text-destructive` (very clinical)
- Technical data attributes (`data-slot`)

### Modal/Dialog Design
**Found in**: `/Users/pedro.figueiredo/Documents/git/neon/platform/packages/design/components/ui/dialog.tsx:47-88`

```typescript
function DialogContent({
  className,
  children,
  showCloseButton = true,
  ...props
}: React.ComponentProps<typeof DialogPrimitive.Content> & {
  showCloseButton?: boolean;
}) {
  return (
