      )}
    </DialogPrimitive.Content>
  );
}
```

**Current formal aspects**:
- Precise positioning (`top-[50%] left-[50%]`)
- Generic close button with technical `sr-only` text
- Very systematic animations (`duration-200`)
- Clean but impersonal styling

### Alert/Notification Patterns
